				<h2 class="subheader">VITAL FORCE / VITALITY</h2>
					Our body is constantly exposed to various external and internal factors. Factors like temperature change, physical and mental strains, exposure to germs, pollutants and other wear and tear. Despite all this, unlike a machine, we rarely fall ill. And when we do the body defends, repairs, develops and functions itself.
					This is the coordinating, defending and dominating force within each of us. This force is commonly known as immunity or the resistance power of our body. Dr. Hahnemann recognized this force of life as Vital Force or Vitality. <br />
				<h2 class="subheader">DISEASE & HOMOEOPATHY</h2>
					When you get fever or cough and cold or say you have a severe headache, what do you describe it as? Normally it is described as a disease. The science of Homoeopathy believes that they are not diseases but bodies expressing internal disharmony. And it is this disharmony that leads to the state of disease. The real sickness is disturbance of the normal functioning of the vital force or vitality. When you take Homeopathic medicines, it harmonizes the internal disharmony and restores the normal health.<br />
				<h2 class="subheader">HOLISTIC APPROACH</h2>
					A human body is a whole unit of various functions which we describe as your head, heart, lungs, etc. Hence when a person falls ill, his whole body is unwell and not just a body part. And as described above, when a person falls ill, it is because of a basic disorder of the vital force. In Homoeopathic treatment we give the patient a single medication to bring about complete wellness. This treats the patient as a whole, removing all ailments.<br />
				<h2 class="subheader">INDIVIDUALIZATION</h2>
					Dr. Hahnemann had concluded that “There are no diseases, there are only sick people”. That is why, in Homoeopathic treatments, every person is studied and treated as an individual. The prescriptions are made for the person and not for the disease that the person is suffering from. So, ten patients with similar diagnosis will receive different medicines whereas ten people with different diagnosis may receive the same medicine.<br />
				<h2 class="subheader">SUPPRESSION</h2>
					The modern medical practitioner treats surface manifestations like discharge or eruptions with local measures. Such treatments make the local manifestations disappear but sooner or later a deeper manifestation arises.<br />
					Homeopathy treats the hidden, suppressed manifestation. Homoeopathic treatments aid the process of elimination of toxins, which leads to cure. After a Homoeopathic treatment, a patient may often develop an increase of natural elimination (stool, urine, sweat) or an unnatural elimination (nasal discharges, leucorrhoea, etc.) or an old suppressed eruption may reappear. The onset of these discharges is generally accompanied by an improvement in the clinical condition of the patient.<br />
			</div>
			<div id="myth" class="about-content bodyContent">
				<h2 class="secondryTitle">MYTHS: WHAT HOMOEOPATHY IS NOT</h2>
				<h2 class="secondryTitle">Homoeopathy is not slow acting:</h2>
				There is a misconception that Homeopathic medicines take a long time to cure. One of the reasons behind this misconception is that patients come to a Homeopath after they have tried other treatments for a long time. By the time they take Homoeopathy the disease is normally at an advanced stage.<br />
				To reverse the pattern of the disease it normally takes some time. People who start treating a disease with Homeopathy get faster results. It is more in the mind that it is slow acting and not in reality.<br />
				<h2 class="secondryTitle">Homeopathy is not placebo effect or faith healing:</h2>
				This is again another misconception that is spread around the medical fraternity. Even chronic cases are treated effectively around the world with Homeopathy. As every patient is treated individually the medicines that treat them are also different. So, ten cases of the same ailment in ten people are treated with different medicines. The principles of Homeopathy differ from other principles, which is why there are misconceptions and bad press about Homeopathy in the medical fraternity.<br />
				<h2 class="secondryTitle">Homoeopathy helps only in chronic cases, not in acute ones:</h2>
				Homoeopathy works as a great alternative therapy. It does wonders in acute cases of cold-cough, fever, otitis, tonsillitis, etc wherein the exact symptoms are noted & a perfectly suited Homoeopathic medicine is prescribed.<br />
			</div>
